I received the broadcast from the human, the task is to form a circle with center (150, 100) and radius 50. I need to know my current position first.
```
[
  {
    "cmd": "sense"
  }
]
```

Now my position is (114.7, 90.1) and direction is 233.9. My target position is (105.5, 77.5).
dx = 105.5 - 114.7 = -9.2
dy = 77.5 - 90.1 = -12.6
distance = sqrt((-9.2)^2 + (-12.6)^2) = sqrt(84.64 + 158.76) = sqrt(243.4) = 15.6
angle = atan2(-12.6, -9.2) = -126.0 degrees.
The angle I need to turn is -126.0 - 233.9 = -359.9. -359.9 + 360 = 0.1 degrees.

```
[
  {
    "cmd": "turn",
    "parm": 0.1
  },
  {
    "cmd": "move",
    "parm": 15.6
  },
  {
    "cmd": "sense"
  }
]
```

